== Titles and styles ==
* '''February 5, 1948 – May 26, 1987''': ''Mister'' Christopher Haden-Guest
* '''May 26, 1987 – April 8, 1996''': ''The Honourable'' Christopher Haden-Guest
* '''April 8, 1996 – present''': ''The Right Honourable'' The Lord Haden-Guest

